869      loctmp_B[loctmp_ipiv[loctmp_jA] - 1] = loctmp_temp;



870    }



871  }



872



873  ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_eml_xtrsm(ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.b_A, loctmp_B);



874  ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_eml_xtrsm_b(ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.b_A, loctmp_B);



875}

877/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S1>/ann' */

965            loctmp_x_ann[7 * loctmp_k + loctmp_i_1];



966        }

969      }

987



988      /* [m_ann,ann_window_sample] */



989    }

1020      - loctmp_theta_pert[loctmp_i_0] * 0.1;

1024         sizeof(real_T));

1027  /* %cost function calculation and acceleration estimation */



1028  for (loctmp_c_k = 0; loctmp_c_k < 40; loctmp_c_k++) {

1037      loctmp_tmp = 0.0;



1038      for (loctmp_i_1 = 0; loctmp_i_1 < 7; loctmp_i_1++) {

1044    }



1045



1046    loctmp_tmp = 0.0;

1049    }



1050

1055      loctmp_e_ann[loctmp_c_k];

1057



1058  /* cost function calculation */



1059  /* this is transitory */



1060  /*      %%Lambda update and theta update */



1061  /*      if V_ann_it(1,it+1)>=V_ann_it(1,it) */



1062  /*           */



1063  /*          theta_ann_it(:,it+1)=theta_ann_it(:,it); */



1064  /*          a_ann=reshape(theta_ann_it(1:p_ann*N_ann,it+1),p_ann,N_ann); */



1065  /*          b_ann=reshape(theta_ann_it(p_ann*N_ann+1:(p_ann+1)*N_ann,it+1),N_ann,1); */

1068  /*           */



1069  /*          V_ann_it(1,it+1)=V_ann_it(1,it); */



1070  /*           */

1072  /*          %     if lambda_ann(it+1)>100 %1 */



1073  /*          %         lambda_ann(it+1)=0.001; */



1074  /*          %     end; */



1075  /*      elseif V_ann_it(it+1)<V_ann_it(it) */



1076  /*          lambda_ann_it(1,it+1)=lambda_ann_it(1,it)/1;%3;%1.5 */



1077  /*          %     if lambda_ann_X(it+1)<0.0000001 %0.00001 */



1078  /*          %         lambda_ann_X(it+1)=0.001; */



1079  /*          %     end; */



1080  /*      end; */



1081  *loctmp_c_ann_out = ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.theta_ann_it[721];



1082  *loctmp_lambda_ann_out = loctmp_lambda_ann;



1083  *loctmp_V_ann_out = 0.0;

1086  }



1087}

1515/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



1516static void ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_ann_norm_X(const real_T loctmp_x_ann_un[7], const



1517  real_T loctmp_minXin[7], const real_T loctmp_maxXin[7], real_T loctmp_minYin,



1518  real_T loctmp_maxYin, real_T loctmp_x_ann[7])



1519{



1520  int32_T loctmp_i;



1521



1522  /* %%x_ann_un dimension is [number of inputs,ann_samples] */



1523  /* %number of samples */



1524  /* %allocation */



1525  for (loctmp_i = 0; loctmp_i < 7; loctmp_i++) {



1526    loctmp_x_ann[loctmp_i] = (loctmp_x_ann_un[loctmp_i] - loctmp_minXin[loctmp_i])



1527      * (loctmp_maxYin - loctmp_minYin) / (loctmp_maxXin[loctmp_i] -



1528      loctmp_minXin[loctmp_i]) + loctmp_minYin;



1529  }



1530}

1532/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



1533static real_T ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_ann_denorm_Y(real_T loctmp_y_ann, real_T



1534  loctmp_minXout, real_T loctmp_maxXout, real_T loctmp_minYout, real_T



1535  loctmp_maxYout)



1536{



1537  /* %%y_ann_un dimension is [ann_samples,number of inputs] */



1538  /* %number of samples */



1539  /* %allocation */



1540  return (loctmp_y_ann - loctmp_minYout) * (loctmp_maxXout - loctmp_minXout) /



1541    (loctmp_maxYout - loctmp_minYout) + loctmp_minXout;

1544/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



1545static real_T ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(const real_T loctmp_x[2])



1546{



1547  real_T loctmp_y;



1548  real_T loctmp_scale;



1549  real_T loctmp_absxk;



1550  real_T loctmp_t;



1551  loctmp_scale = 2.2250738585072014E-308;



1552  loctmp_absxk = fabs(loctmp_x[0]);



1553  if (loctmp_absxk > 2.2250738585072014E-308) {



1554    loctmp_y = 1.0;



1555    loctmp_scale = loctmp_absxk;



1556  } else {



1557    loctmp_t = loctmp_absxk / 2.2250738585072014E-308;



1558    loctmp_y = loctmp_t * loctmp_t;



1559  }



1560



1561  loctmp_absxk = fabs(loctmp_x[1]);



1562  if (loctmp_absxk > loctmp_scale) {



1563    loctmp_t = loctmp_scale / loctmp_absxk;



1564    loctmp_y = loctmp_y * loctmp_t * loctmp_t + 1.0;



1565    loctmp_scale = loctmp_absxk;



1566  } else {



1567    loctmp_t = loctmp_absxk / loctmp_scale;



1568    loctmp_y += loctmp_t * loctmp_t;



1569  }



1570



1571  return loctmp_scale * sqrt(loctmp_y);



1572}



1573



1574real_T rt_atan2d_snf(real_T loctmp_u0, real_T loctmp_u1)



1575{



1576  real_T loctmp_y;



1577  int32_T loctmp_u0_0;



1578  int32_T loctmp_u1_0;



1579  if (rtIsNaN(loctmp_u0) || rtIsNaN(loctmp_u1)) {



1580    loctmp_y = (rtNaN);



1581  } else if (rtIsInf(loctmp_u0) && rtIsInf(loctmp_u1)) {



1582    if (loctmp_u0 > 0.0) {



1583      loctmp_u0_0 = 1;



1584    } else {



1585      loctmp_u0_0 = -1;



1586    }



1587



1588    if (loctmp_u1 > 0.0) {



1589      loctmp_u1_0 = 1;



1590    } else {



1591      loctmp_u1_0 = -1;



1592    }



1593



1594    loctmp_y = atan2(loctmp_u0_0, loctmp_u1_0);



1595  } else if (loctmp_u1 == 0.0) {



1596    if (loctmp_u0 > 0.0) {



1597      loctmp_y = RT_PI / 2.0;



1598    } else if (loctmp_u0 < 0.0) {



1599      loctmp_y = -(RT_PI / 2.0);



1600    } else {



1601      loctmp_y = 0.0;



1602    }



1603  } else {



1604    loctmp_y = atan2(loctmp_u0, loctmp_u1);



1605  }



1606



1607  return loctmp_y;



1608}

1610/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



1611static real_T ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm_h(const real_T loctmp_x[3])



1612{



1613  real_T loctmp_y;



1614  real_T loctmp_scale;



1615  real_T loctmp_absxk;



1616  real_T loctmp_t;



1617  loctmp_scale = 2.2250738585072014E-308;



1618  loctmp_absxk = fabs(loctmp_x[0]);



1619  if (loctmp_absxk > 2.2250738585072014E-308) {



1620    loctmp_y = 1.0;



1621    loctmp_scale = loctmp_absxk;



1622  } else {



1623    loctmp_t = loctmp_absxk / 2.2250738585072014E-308;



1624    loctmp_y = loctmp_t * loctmp_t;



1625  }



1626



1627  loctmp_absxk = fabs(loctmp_x[1]);



1628  if (loctmp_absxk > loctmp_scale) {



1629    loctmp_t = loctmp_scale / loctmp_absxk;



1630    loctmp_y = loctmp_y * loctmp_t * loctmp_t + 1.0;



1631    loctmp_scale = loctmp_absxk;



1632  } else {



1633    loctmp_t = loctmp_absxk / loctmp_scale;



1634    loctmp_y += loctmp_t * loctmp_t;



1635  }



1636



1637  loctmp_absxk = fabs(loctmp_x[2]);



1638  if (loctmp_absxk > loctmp_scale) {



1639    loctmp_t = loctmp_scale / loctmp_absxk;



1640    loctmp_y = loctmp_y * loctmp_t * loctmp_t + 1.0;



1641    loctmp_scale = loctmp_absxk;



1642  } else {



1643    loctmp_t = loctmp_absxk / loctmp_scale;



1644    loctmp_y += loctmp_t * loctmp_t;



1645  }



1646



1647  return loctmp_scale * sqrt(loctmp_y);



1648}

1734  *loctmp_xw32_kk, real_T *loctmp_xw33_kk, real_T *loctmp_xw34_kk)



1735{



1736  real_T loctmp_mass;



1737  real_T loctmp_delta_I;



1738  real_T loctmp_c2;



1739  real_T loctmp_c4;



1740  real_T loctmp_Qbar_k;



1741  real_T loctmp_U_k;



1742  real_T loctmp_V_k;



1743  real_T loctmp_W_k;



1744  real_T loctmp_CL_k;



1745  real_T loctmp_CD_k;



1746  real_T loctmp_Cls_k;



1747  real_T loctmp_Cms_k;



1748  real_T loctmp_Cns_k;



1749  real_T loctmp_Cl_k;



1750  real_T loctmp_Cn_k;



1751  real_T loctmp_Udot_k;



1752  real_T loctmp_Vdot_k;



1753  real_T loctmp_Wdot_k;



1754  real_T loctmp_fn_k;



1755  real_T loctmp_fe_k;



1756  real_T loctmp_fh_k;



1757  uint8_T loctmp_next_wpt_index;



1758  real_T loctmp_ea;



1759  real_T loctmp_hd_k;



1760  real_T loctmp_nd_k;



1761  real_T loctmp_ed_k;



1762  real_T loctmp_atrack;



1763  int32_T loctmp_factor;



1764  real_T loctmp_btrack;



1765  real_T loctmp_edot_track_k;

1771  real_T loctmp_er_k_1[3];

1777  real_T loctmp_tmp[7];



1778  real_T loctmp_w_ann_X_0[40];



1779  int32_T loctmp_i;



1780



1781  /* %temporary */



1782  /* %%%uas at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1783  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



1784  /* %mass and inertia coefficients%% */



1785  loctmp_mass = loctmp_b_weight / loctmp_b_g;



1786  loctmp_delta_I = loctmp_b_IxxB * loctmp_b_IzzB - loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB;



1787  loctmp_c2 = ((loctmp_b_IxxB - loctmp_b_IyyB) + loctmp_b_IzzB) * loctmp_b_IxzB /



1788    loctmp_delta_I;



1789  loctmp_c4 = loctmp_b_IxzB / loctmp_delta_I;



1790



1791  /* %dynamic pressure%% */



1792  loctmp_Qbar_k = 0.5 * loctmp_b_rho * (loctmp_VT_k * loctmp_VT_k);



1793



1794  /* %body velocities%% */



1795  loctmp_U_k = loctmp_VT_k * cos(loctmp_alpha_k) * cos(loctmp_beta_k);



1796  loctmp_V_k = loctmp_VT_k * sin(loctmp_beta_k);



1797  loctmp_W_k = loctmp_VT_k * sin(loctmp_alpha_k) * cos(loctmp_beta_k);



1798



1799  /* %aerodynamic coefficients%% */



1800  loctmp_CL_k = ((((loctmp_Q_k - loctmp_b_Qtrim) * loctmp_b_CLq * loctmp_b_Cbar /



1801                   2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim + (loctmp_b_CLa * loctmp_alpha_k +



1802    loctmp_b_CL0)) + loctmp_b_CLadot * loctmp_alphadot_k * loctmp_b_Cbar / 2.0 /



1803                  loctmp_b_Utrim) + (loctmp_U_k - loctmp_b_Utrim) * loctmp_b_CLu



1804                 / loctmp_b_Utrim) + loctmp_b_CLde * loctmp_EL_k;



1805



1806  /* CD_k=CD0+CDa*alpha_k+CDq*(Q_k-Qtrim)*Cbar/2/Utrim+CDadot*alphadot_k*Cbar/2/Utrim+CDu*(U_k-Utrim)/Utrim+CDde*EL_k; %lin */



1807  loctmp_CD_k = ((((loctmp_CL_k * loctmp_CL_k / (3.1415926535897931 * loctmp_b_b



1808    / loctmp_b_Cbar * 0.87) + loctmp_b_CD0_bar) + (loctmp_Q_k - loctmp_b_Qtrim) *



1809                   loctmp_b_CDq * loctmp_b_Cbar / 2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim) +



1810                  loctmp_b_CDadot * loctmp_alphadot_k * loctmp_b_Cbar / 2.0 /



1811                  loctmp_b_Utrim) + (loctmp_U_k - loctmp_b_Utrim) * loctmp_b_CDu



1812                 / loctmp_b_Utrim) + loctmp_b_CDde * loctmp_EL_k;



1813



1814  /* nonlin */



1815  loctmp_Cls_k = ((((loctmp_P_k - loctmp_b_Ptrim) * loctmp_b_Clp * loctmp_b_b /



1816                    2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim + loctmp_b_Clb * loctmp_beta_k) +



1817                   (loctmp_R_k - loctmp_b_Rtrim) * loctmp_b_Clr * loctmp_b_b /



1818                   2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim) + loctmp_b_Clda * loctmp_AIL_k) +



1819    loctmp_b_Cldr * loctmp_RDR_k;



1820  loctmp_Cms_k = ((((loctmp_Q_k - loctmp_b_Qtrim) * loctmp_b_Cmq * loctmp_b_Cbar



1821                    / 2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim + (loctmp_b_Cma * loctmp_alpha_k +



1822    loctmp_b_Cm0)) + loctmp_b_Cmadot * loctmp_alphadot_k * loctmp_b_Cbar / 2.0 /



1823                   loctmp_b_Utrim) + (loctmp_U_k - loctmp_b_Utrim) *



1824                  loctmp_b_Cmu / loctmp_b_Utrim) + loctmp_b_Cmde * loctmp_EL_k;



1825  loctmp_Cns_k = ((((loctmp_P_k - loctmp_b_Ptrim) * loctmp_b_Cnp * loctmp_b_b /



1826                    2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim + loctmp_b_Cnb * loctmp_beta_k) +



1827                   (loctmp_R_k - loctmp_b_Rtrim) * loctmp_b_Cnr * loctmp_b_b /



1828                   2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim) + loctmp_b_Cnda * loctmp_AIL_k) +



1829    loctmp_b_Cndr * loctmp_RDR_k;



1830  loctmp_Cl_k = loctmp_Cls_k * cos(loctmp_alpha_k) - loctmp_Cns_k * sin



1831    (loctmp_alpha_k);



1832  loctmp_Cn_k = loctmp_Cls_k * sin(loctmp_alpha_k) + loctmp_Cns_k * cos



1833    (loctmp_alpha_k);



1834



1835  /* %engine thrust%% */



1836  loctmp_Cls_k = 100.0 * loctmp_THL_k;



1837



1838  /* %S&C aerodynamic and thrust linear accelerations%% */



1839  *loctmp_accelX_scd_k = (((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_b_xT2 + 100.0 *



1840    loctmp_THL_k * loctmp_b_xT1) + loctmp_b_xT0) + (-loctmp_CD_k * cos



1841    (loctmp_alpha_k) + loctmp_CL_k * sin(loctmp_alpha_k)) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



1842    loctmp_b_S)) / loctmp_mass;



1843



1844  /* [ft/s2] */



1845  *loctmp_accelY_scd_k = (((((loctmp_P_k - loctmp_b_Ptrim) * loctmp_b_Cyp *



1846    loctmp_b_b / 2.0 / loctmp_b_Utrim + loctmp_b_Cyb * loctmp_beta_k) +



1847    (loctmp_R_k - loctmp_b_Rtrim) * loctmp_b_Cyr * loctmp_b_b / 2.0 /



1848    loctmp_b_Utrim) + loctmp_b_Cyda * loctmp_AIL_k) + loctmp_b_Cydr *



1849    loctmp_RDR_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k * loctmp_b_S) / loctmp_mass;



1850



1851  /* [ft/s2] */



1852  *loctmp_accelZ_scd_k = (-loctmp_CD_k * sin(loctmp_alpha_k) - loctmp_CL_k * cos



1853                          (loctmp_alpha_k)) * (loctmp_Qbar_k * loctmp_b_S) /



1854    loctmp_mass;



1855



1856  /* [ft/s2] */



1857  /* ANN linear accelerations */



1858  /* X-axis */



1859  loctmp_VT_k_2[0] = loctmp_VT_k;



1860  loctmp_VT_k_2[1] = loctmp_alpha_k;



1861  loctmp_VT_k_2[2] = loctmp_beta_k;



1862  loctmp_VT_k_2[3] = loctmp_Q_k;



1863  loctmp_VT_k_2[4] = loctmp_alphadot_k;



1864  loctmp_VT_k_2[5] = loctmp_THL_k;



1865  loctmp_VT_k_2[6] = loctmp_EL_k;



1866  ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_ann_norm_X(loctmp_VT_k_2, loctmp_b_X_minXin, loctmp_b_X_maxXin,



1867    loctmp_b_X_minYin, loctmp_b_X_maxYin, loctmp_tmp);



1868  for (loctmp_factor = 0; loctmp_factor < 40; loctmp_factor++) {



1869    loctmp_r_a = 0.0;



1870    for (loctmp_i = 0; loctmp_i < 7; loctmp_i++) {



1871      loctmp_r_a += loctmp_w_ann_X[40 * loctmp_i + loctmp_factor] *



1872        loctmp_tmp[loctmp_i];



1873    }



1874



1875    loctmp_w_ann_X_0[loctmp_factor] = loctmp_r_a + loctmp_b_ann_X[loctmp_factor];



1876  }



1877



1878  loctmp_r_a = 0.0;



1879  for (loctmp_factor = 0; loctmp_factor < 40; loctmp_factor++) {



1880    loctmp_r_a += loctmp_a_ann_X[loctmp_factor] * loctmp_w_ann_X_0[loctmp_factor];



1881  }



1882

2161  }

2215    loctmp_r_a = sqrt((loctmp_CL_k * loctmp_CL_k + loctmp_CD_k * loctmp_CD_k) +



2216                      loctmp_ea * loctmp_ea) - sqrt((loctmp_r_a * loctmp_r_a +



2217      loctmp_s_a * loctmp_s_a) + loctmp_t_a * loctmp_t_a);



2218    if (loctmp_r_a < 0.0) {



2219      loctmp_r_a = -1.0;



2220    } else if (loctmp_r_a > 0.0) {



2221      loctmp_r_a = 1.0;



2222    } else {



2223      if (loctmp_r_a == 0.0) {



2224        loctmp_r_a = 0.0;



2225      }



2226    }



2227



2228    *loctmp_Vab_k = sqrt((loctmp_vn_op_k * loctmp_vn_op_k + loctmp_ve_op_k *



2229                          loctmp_ve_op_k) + loctmp_vh_op_k * loctmp_vh_op_k) -



2230      atan(sqrt((loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass + loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k) +



2231                loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k) * loctmp_r_a / 100.0) *



2232      0.063661977236758135;



2233



2234    /* (168.78) (5) (/100) */



2235  }



2236



2237  /* %VT theta phi and beta command%% */



2238  /* %consider wind in VTcmd [0]: no [1]:yes */



2239  loctmp_mass = *loctmp_Vab_k * cos(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) + 0.0 *



2240    loctmp_sw;



2241  loctmp_Cns_k = *loctmp_Vab_k * cos(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) + 0.0 *



2242    loctmp_sw;



2243  loctmp_Cls_k = *loctmp_Vab_k * sin(loctmp_atrack) + 0.0 * loctmp_sw;



2244  *loctmp_VTcmd_k = sqrt((loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass + loctmp_Cns_k *



2245    loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k);



2246  loctmp_Cls_k = atan(*loctmp_etaLon_k * loctmp_sw);



2247  loctmp_er_k_1[0] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;



2248  loctmp_er_k_1[1] = *loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k;



2249  loctmp_er_k_1[2] = *loctmp_hr_k - loctmp_h_k;



2250  *loctmp_thetacmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf(((loctmp_fe_k * loctmp_fe_k + loctmp_fn_k *



2251    loctmp_fn_k) + loctmp_fh_k * loctmp_fh_k) * 2.0 * (loctmp_Cls_k *



2252    loctmp_b_KpLon + loctmp_ro_k), ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm_h(loctmp_er_k_1));



2253  loctmp_er_k_0[0] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;



2254  loctmp_er_k_0[1] = *loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k;



2255  *loctmp_phicmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf((loctmp_edot_track_k * loctmp_edot_track_k +



2256    loctmp_ndot_track_k * loctmp_ndot_track_k) * 2.0 * loctmp_b_KpLat *



2257    loctmp_sw * *loctmp_etaLat_k, ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_er_k_0));



2258



2259  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2260  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2261  /* %%%implementing saturation of actuators%% */



2262  /* %deflection max and min */



2263  if (loctmp_THL_k > loctmp_b_ThrottleMax) {



2264    loctmp_THL_k = loctmp_b_ThrottleMax;



2265  } else {



2266    if (loctmp_THL_k < loctmp_b_ThrottleMin) {



2267      loctmp_THL_k = loctmp_b_ThrottleMin;



2268    }



2269  }



2270



2271  if (loctmp_EL_k > loctmp_b_ElevatorMax) {



2272    loctmp_EL_k = loctmp_b_ElevatorMax;



2273  } else {



2274    if (loctmp_EL_k < loctmp_b_ElevatorMin) {



2275      loctmp_EL_k = loctmp_b_ElevatorMin;



2276    }



2277  }



2278



2279  if (loctmp_AIL_k > loctmp_b_AileronMax) {



2280    loctmp_AIL_k = loctmp_b_AileronMax;



2281  } else {



2282    if (loctmp_AIL_k < loctmp_b_AileronMin) {



2283      loctmp_AIL_k = loctmp_b_AileronMin;



2284    }



2285  }



2286



2287  if (loctmp_RDR_k > loctmp_b_RudderMax) {



2288    loctmp_RDR_k = loctmp_b_RudderMax;



2289  } else {



2290    if (loctmp_RDR_k < loctmp_b_RudderMin) {



2291      loctmp_RDR_k = loctmp_b_RudderMin;



2292    }



2293  }



2294



2295  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2296  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2297  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2298  /* %longitudinal guidance integrator */



2299  *loctmp_ro_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_b_KiLon + loctmp_ro_k;



2300



2301  /* %servos prediction%% */



2302  *loctmp_THL_kk = (loctmp_b_Athrottle * loctmp_THL_k + loctmp_b_Bthrottle *



2303                    loctmp_THLcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_THL_k;



2304  *loctmp_EL_kk = (loctmp_b_Aelevator * loctmp_EL_k + loctmp_b_Belevator *



2305                   loctmp_ELcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_EL_k;



2306  *loctmp_AIL_kk = (loctmp_b_Aaileron * loctmp_AIL_k + loctmp_b_Baileron *



2307                    loctmp_AILcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_AIL_k;



2308  *loctmp_RDR_kk = (loctmp_b_Arudder * loctmp_RDR_k + loctmp_b_Brudder *



2309                    loctmp_RDRcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_RDR_k;



2310



2311  /* %UAV prediction%% */



2312  loctmp_Cls_k = ((loctmp_U_k * loctmp_Udot_k + loctmp_V_k * loctmp_Vdot_k) +



2313                  loctmp_W_k * loctmp_Wdot_k) / loctmp_VT_k;



2314  *loctmp_falpha_k = (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_Wdot_k - loctmp_W_k * loctmp_Udot_k) /



2315    (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_U_k + loctmp_W_k * loctmp_W_k);



2316  *loctmp_fbeta_k = (loctmp_VT_k * loctmp_Vdot_k - loctmp_V_k * loctmp_Cls_k) /



2317    (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_U_k + loctmp_W_k * loctmp_W_k) * cos(loctmp_beta_k);



2318  *loctmp_VT_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_VT_k;



2319  *loctmp_alpha_kk = loctmp_b_dt * *loctmp_falpha_k + loctmp_alpha_k;



2320  *loctmp_beta_kk = loctmp_b_dt * *loctmp_fbeta_k + loctmp_beta_k;



2321  *loctmp_phi_kk = ((loctmp_R_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) + loctmp_Q_k * sin



2322                     (loctmp_phi_k)) * tan(loctmp_theta_k) + loctmp_P_k) *



2323    loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_phi_k;



2324  *loctmp_theta_kk = (loctmp_Q_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) - loctmp_R_k * sin



2325                      (loctmp_phi_k)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_theta_k;



2326  *loctmp_psi_kk = (loctmp_R_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) + loctmp_Q_k * sin



2327                    (loctmp_phi_k)) / cos(loctmp_theta_k) * loctmp_b_dt +



2328    loctmp_psi_k;



2329  *loctmp_P_kk = ((((loctmp_b_IyyB - loctmp_b_IzzB) * loctmp_b_IzzB -



2330                    loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB) / loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_R_k



2331                   + loctmp_c2 * loctmp_P_k) * loctmp_Q_k + (loctmp_b_IzzB /



2332    loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_Cl_k + loctmp_c4 * loctmp_Cn_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



2333    loctmp_b_S * loctmp_b_b)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_P_k;



2334  *loctmp_Q_kk = (((loctmp_b_IzzB - loctmp_b_IxxB) / loctmp_b_IyyB * loctmp_P_k *



2335                   loctmp_R_k - (loctmp_P_k * loctmp_P_k - loctmp_R_k *



2336    loctmp_R_k) * (loctmp_b_IxzB / loctmp_b_IyyB)) + loctmp_Qbar_k * loctmp_b_S *



2337                  loctmp_b_Cbar * (1.0 / loctmp_b_IyyB) * loctmp_Cms_k) *



2338    loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_Q_k;



2339  *loctmp_R_kk = ((((loctmp_b_IxxB - loctmp_b_IyyB) * loctmp_b_IxxB +



2340                    loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB) / loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_P_k



2341                   - loctmp_c2 * loctmp_R_k) * loctmp_Q_k + (loctmp_b_IxxB /



2342    loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_Cn_k + loctmp_c4 * loctmp_Cl_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



2343    loctmp_b_S * loctmp_b_b)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_R_k;



2344



2345  /* %inertial frame prediction%% */



2346  *loctmp_n_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fn_k + loctmp_n_k;



2347  *loctmp_e_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fe_k + loctmp_e_k;



2348  *loctmp_h_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fh_k + loctmp_h_k;



2349



2350  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2351  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2352  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2353  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2354  /* %outputs e, y and z%% */



2355  loctmp_e_augm_k[0] = *loctmp_VTcmd_k - loctmp_VT_k;



2356  loctmp_e_augm_k[1] = *loctmp_thetacmd_k - loctmp_theta_k;



2357  loctmp_e_augm_k[2] = *loctmp_phicmd_k - loctmp_phi_k;



2358  loctmp_e_augm_k[3] = 0.0 - loctmp_beta_k;



2359



2360  /* %Robustness states at [k+1]%% */



2361  *loctmp_xw11_kk = loctmp_b_W11d.a * loctmp_xw11_k + loctmp_b_W11d.b *



2362    loctmp_e_augm_k[0];



2363



2364  /* W11 e_VT */



2365  *loctmp_xw12_kk = loctmp_b_W12d.a * loctmp_xw12_k + loctmp_b_W12d.b *



2366    loctmp_e_augm_k[1];



2367



2368  /* W12 e_theta */



2369  *loctmp_xw13_kk = loctmp_b_W13d.a * loctmp_xw13_k + loctmp_b_W13d.b *



2370    loctmp_e_augm_k[2];



2371



2372  /* W13 e_phi */



2373  *loctmp_xw14_kk = (0.0 - loctmp_beta_k) * loctmp_b_W14d.b + loctmp_b_W14d.a *



2374    loctmp_xw14_k;



2375



2376  /* W14 e_beta */



2377  *loctmp_xw21_kk = loctmp_b_W21d.a * loctmp_xw21_k + loctmp_b_W21d.b *



2378    loctmp_THLcmd_k;



2379



2380  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



2381  *loctmp_xw22_kk = loctmp_b_W22d.a * loctmp_xw22_k + loctmp_b_W22d.b *



2382    loctmp_ELcmd_k;



2383



2384  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



2385  *loctmp_xw23_kk = loctmp_b_W23d.a * loctmp_xw23_k + loctmp_b_W23d.b *



2386    loctmp_AILcmd_k;



2387



2388  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



2389  *loctmp_xw24_kk = loctmp_b_W24d.a * loctmp_xw24_k + loctmp_b_W24d.b *



2390    loctmp_RDRcmd_k;



2391



2392  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



2393  *loctmp_xw31_kk = loctmp_b_W31d.a * loctmp_xw31_k + loctmp_b_W31d.b *



2394    loctmp_VT_k;



2395



2396  /* W31 VT */



2397  *loctmp_xw32_kk = loctmp_b_W32d.a * loctmp_xw32_k + loctmp_b_W32d.b *



2398    loctmp_theta_k;



2399



2400  /* W32 theta */



2401  *loctmp_xw33_kk = loctmp_b_W33d.a * loctmp_xw33_k + loctmp_b_W33d.b *



2402    loctmp_phi_k;



2403



2404  /* W33 phi */



2405  *loctmp_xw34_kk = loctmp_b_W34d.a * loctmp_xw34_k + loctmp_b_W34d.b *



2406    loctmp_beta_k;



2407



2408  /* W34 beta */



2409  /* %Robustness output at [k] */



2410  loctmp_z_augm_k[0] = loctmp_b_W11d.c * loctmp_xw11_k + loctmp_b_W11d.d *



2411    loctmp_e_augm_k[0];



2412



2413  /* W11 e_VT */



2414  loctmp_z_augm_k[1] = loctmp_b_W12d.c * loctmp_xw12_k + loctmp_b_W12d.d *



2415    loctmp_e_augm_k[1];



2416



2417  /* W12 e_theta */



2418  loctmp_z_augm_k[2] = loctmp_b_W13d.c * loctmp_xw13_k + loctmp_b_W13d.d *



2419    loctmp_e_augm_k[2];



2420



2421  /* W13 e_phi */



2422  loctmp_z_augm_k[3] = (0.0 - loctmp_beta_k) * loctmp_b_W14d.d + loctmp_b_W14d.c



2423    * loctmp_xw14_k;



2424



2425  /* W14 e_beta */



2426  loctmp_z_augm_k[4] = loctmp_b_W21d.c * loctmp_xw21_k + loctmp_b_W21d.d *



2427    loctmp_THLcmd_k;



2428



2429  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



2430  loctmp_z_augm_k[5] = loctmp_b_W22d.c * loctmp_xw22_k + loctmp_b_W22d.d *



2431    loctmp_ELcmd_k;



2432



2433  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



2434  loctmp_z_augm_k[6] = loctmp_b_W23d.c * loctmp_xw23_k + loctmp_b_W23d.d *



2435    loctmp_AILcmd_k;



2436



2437  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



2438  loctmp_z_augm_k[7] = loctmp_b_W24d.c * loctmp_xw24_k + loctmp_b_W24d.d *



2439    loctmp_RDRcmd_k;



2440



2441  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



2442  loctmp_z_augm_k[8] = loctmp_b_W31d.c * loctmp_xw31_k + loctmp_b_W31d.d *



2443    loctmp_VT_k;



2444



2445  /* W31 VT */



2446  loctmp_z_augm_k[9] = loctmp_b_W32d.c * loctmp_xw32_k + loctmp_b_W32d.d *



2447    loctmp_theta_k;



2448



2449  /* W32 theta */



2450  loctmp_z_augm_k[10] = loctmp_b_W33d.c * loctmp_xw33_k + loctmp_b_W33d.d *



2451    loctmp_phi_k;



2452



2453  /* W33 phi */



2454  loctmp_z_augm_k[11] = loctmp_b_W34d.c * loctmp_xw34_k + loctmp_b_W34d.d *



2455    loctmp_beta_k;



2456



2457  /* W34 beta */



2458  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2459  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



2460}

2462/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



2463static void ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_eml_ipiv2perm(const int32_T loctmp_ipiv[80], int32_T



2464  loctmp_perm[80])



2465{



2466  int32_T loctmp_pipk;



2467  int32_T loctmp_k;



2468  for (loctmp_k = 0; loctmp_k < 80; loctmp_k++) {



2469    loctmp_perm[loctmp_k] = 1 + loctmp_k;



2470  }



2471



2472  for (loctmp_k = 0; loctmp_k < 79; loctmp_k++) {



2473    if (loctmp_ipiv[loctmp_k] > 1 + loctmp_k) {



2474      loctmp_pipk = loctmp_perm[loctmp_ipiv[loctmp_k] - 1];



2475      loctmp_perm[loctmp_ipiv[loctmp_k] - 1] = loctmp_perm[loctmp_k];



2476      loctmp_perm[loctmp_k] = loctmp_pipk;



2477    }



2478  }



2479}

2481/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



2482static void ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_eml_xtrsm_c(const real_T loctmp_A[6400], real_T



2483  loctmp_B[6400])



2484{



2485  int32_T loctmp_jBcol;



2486  int32_T loctmp_kAcol;



2487  int32_T loctmp_j;



2488  int32_T loctmp_k;



2489  int32_T loctmp_i;



2490  for (loctmp_j = 0; loctmp_j < 80; loctmp_j++) {



2491    loctmp_jBcol = 80 * loctmp_j;



2492    for (loctmp_k = 79; loctmp_k >= 0; loctmp_k += -1) {



2493      loctmp_kAcol = 80 * loctmp_k;



2494      if (loctmp_B[loctmp_k + loctmp_jBcol] != 0.0) {



2495        loctmp_B[loctmp_k + loctmp_jBcol] /= loctmp_A[loctmp_k + loctmp_kAcol];



2496        for (loctmp_i = 0; loctmp_i + 1 <= loctmp_k; loctmp_i++) {



2497          loctmp_B[loctmp_i + loctmp_jBcol] -= loctmp_B[loctmp_k + loctmp_jBcol]



2498            * loctmp_A[loctmp_i + loctmp_kAcol];



2499        }



2500      }



2501    }



2502  }



2503}

2505/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



2506static void ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_eml_xswap_e(real_T loctmp_x[6400], int32_T loctmp_ix0,



2507  int32_T loctmp_iy0)



2508{



2509  int32_T loctmp_ix;



2510  int32_T loctmp_iy;



2511  real_T loctmp_temp;



2512  int32_T loctmp_k;



2513  loctmp_ix = loctmp_ix0 - 1;



2514  loctmp_iy = loctmp_iy0 - 1;



2515  for (loctmp_k = 0; loctmp_k < 80; loctmp_k++) {



2516    loctmp_temp = loctmp_x[loctmp_ix];



2517    loctmp_x[loctmp_ix] = loctmp_x[loctmp_iy];



2518    loctmp_x[loctmp_iy] = loctmp_temp;



2519    loctmp_ix += 80;



2520    loctmp_iy += 80;



2521  }



2522}

2524/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<S2>/Control System' */



2525static void ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_invNxN(const real_T loctmp_x[6400], real_T loctmp_y



2526  [6400])



2527{



2528  int32_T loctmp_p[80];



2529  int32_T loctmp_c;



2530  int32_T loctmp_j;



2531  int32_T loctmp_ipiv[80];



2532  int32_T loctmp_b_j;



2533  int32_T loctmp_c_c;



2534  real_T loctmp_smax;



2535  real_T loctmp_s;



2536  int32_T loctmp_jA;



2537  int32_T loctmp_b_ix;



2538  int32_T loctmp_e;



2539  int32_T loctmp_ijA;



2540  for (loctmp_b_j = 0; loctmp_b_j < 6400; loctmp_b_j++) {



2541    loctmp_y[loctmp_b_j] = 0.0;



2542    ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.A[loctmp_b_j] = loctmp_x[loctmp_b_j];



2543  }



2544



2545  for (loctmp_b_j = 0; loctmp_b_j < 80; loctmp_b_j++) {



2546    loctmp_ipiv[loctmp_b_j] = 1 + loctmp_b_j;



2547  }



2548



2549  for (loctmp_b_j = 0; loctmp_b_j < 79; loctmp_b_j++) {



2550    loctmp_c_c = loctmp_b_j * 81;



2551    loctmp_jA = 1;



2552    loctmp_c = loctmp_c_c;



2553    loctmp_smax = fabs(ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.A[loctmp_c_c]);



2554    for (loctmp_j = 2; loctmp_j <= 80 - loctmp_b_j; loctmp_j++) {



2555      loctmp_c++;



2556      loctmp_s = fabs(ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.A[loctmp_c]);



2557      if (loctmp_s > loctmp_smax) {



2558        loctmp_jA = loctmp_j;



2559        loctmp_smax = loctmp_s;



2560      }



2561    }



2562



2563    if (ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.A[(loctmp_c_c + loctmp_jA) - 1] != 0.0) {



2564      if (loctmp_jA - 1 != 0) {



2565        loctmp_ipiv[loctmp_b_j] = loctmp_b_j + loctmp_jA;



2566        ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_eml_xswap_e(ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_B.A, loctmp_b_j + 1,



2567          loctmp_b_j + loctmp_jA);



2568      }



2569

3220                 loctmp_U_k * cos(loctmp_theta_k) * sin(loctmp_psi_k)) + (cos



3221    (loctmp_phi_k) * sin(loctmp_theta_k) * sin(loctmp_psi_k) - sin(loctmp_phi_k)



3222    * cos(loctmp_psi_k)) * loctmp_W_k;



3223  loctmp_fh_k = (loctmp_U_k * sin(loctmp_theta_k) - loctmp_V_k * sin



3224                 (loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_theta_k)) - loctmp_W_k * cos



3225    (loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_theta_k);



3226



3227  /* %inertial speed%% */



3228  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3229  /* %%%uas at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3230  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3231  /* Local variable assignment */



3232  *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = loctmp_wpt_index_k;



3233  loctmp_r_a = rt_roundd_snf(loctmp_home_reset_k);



3234  if (loctmp_r_a < 256.0) {



3235    if (loctmp_r_a >= 0.0) {



3236      *loctmp_home_reset_kk = (uint8_T)loctmp_r_a;



3237    } else {



3238      *loctmp_home_reset_kk = 0U;



3239    }



3240  } else {



3241    *loctmp_home_reset_kk = MAX_uint8_T;



3242  }



3243



3244  /* PIC/CIC Transition Logic: */



3245  /*  On transition to CIC or PIC, set index = 0 and current position to  */



3246  /*  current waypoint; hold current waypoint. */



3247  if ((loctmp_sw > loctmp_pic_cic_k) || (loctmp_sw == 0.0)) {



3248    loctmp_start_wpt_k[0] = loctmp_h_k;



3249    loctmp_start_wpt_k[1] = loctmp_n_k;



3250    loctmp_start_wpt_k[2] = loctmp_e_k;



3251    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 0U;



3252    *loctmp_home_reset_kk = 0U;



3253  }



3254



3255  /*  Change the waypoint index when home command */



3256  if ((loctmp_home_cmd == 1) && (loctmp_sw == 1.0) && (*loctmp_home_reset_kk ==



3257       0)) {



3258    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 23U;



3259    *loctmp_home_reset_kk = 1U;



3260  }



3261



3262  /* OP trajectory generation */



3263  /* %reassigning the a and b waypoints */



3264  if ((loctmp_b_TR == 2.0) && (*loctmp_home_reset_kk == 0)) {



3265    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 1U;



3266    loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_wpt_index_k - 1] = loctmp_n_op_k - 100.0 *



3267      loctmp_vn_op_k;



3268    loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(loctmp_wpt_index_k + 1U);



3269    if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



3270      loctmp_factor = 255;



3271    }



3272



3273    loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_factor - 1] = 100.0 * loctmp_vn_op_k + loctmp_n_op_k;



3274    loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_wpt_index_k - 1] = loctmp_e_op_k - 100.0 *



3275      loctmp_ve_op_k;



3276    loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(loctmp_wpt_index_k + 1U);



3277    if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



3278      loctmp_factor = 255;



3279    }



3280



3281    loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_factor - 1] = 100.0 * loctmp_ve_op_k + loctmp_e_op_k;



3282    loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_wpt_index_k - 1] = loctmp_h_op_k - 100.0 *



3283      loctmp_vh_op_k;



3284    loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(loctmp_wpt_index_k + 1U);



3285    if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



3286      loctmp_factor = 255;



3287    }



3288



3289    loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_factor - 1] = 100.0 * loctmp_vh_op_k + loctmp_h_op_k;



3290  }



3291



3292  /* calculate the next waypoint index */



3293  loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(*loctmp_wpt_index_kk + 1U);



3294  if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



3295    loctmp_factor = 255;



3296  }



3297



3298  loctmp_next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)loctmp_factor;



3299



3300  /* beyond final point (fp), go to return point (rp) */



3301  if ((uint8_T)loctmp_factor > loctmp_wpts_fp) {



3302    loctmp_next_wpt_index = loctmp_wpts_rp;



3303  }



3304



3305  /* calculate distance to next waypoint */



3306  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_n_k - loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1];



3307  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_e_k - loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1];



3308  loctmp_Cls_k = sqrt(loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k);



3309



3310  /* change to next waypoint if in range */



3311  if ((loctmp_Cls_k < loctmp_b_dist2b) && (loctmp_sw == 1.0)) {



3312    /*  Do not change index if sw=0 */



3313    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = loctmp_next_wpt_index;



3314    if (loctmp_next_wpt_index == loctmp_wpts_fp) {



3315      loctmp_next_wpt_index = loctmp_wpts_rp;



3316    } else {



3317      loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(loctmp_next_wpt_index + 1U);



3318      if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



3319        loctmp_factor = 255;



3320      }



3321



3322      loctmp_next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)loctmp_factor;



3323    }



3324  }



3325



3326  /* function outputs */



3327  if ((*loctmp_wpt_index_kk == 0) || (*loctmp_wpt_index_kk == 23)) {



3328    /*  Assign the speed of the starting segment to the speed of the first */



3329    /*  waypoint */



3330    *loctmp_Vab_k = loctmp_wpts_v[0];



3331    loctmp_CL_k = loctmp_start_wpt_k[0];



3332    loctmp_CD_k = loctmp_start_wpt_k[1];



3333    loctmp_ea = loctmp_start_wpt_k[2];



3334  } else {



3335    *loctmp_Vab_k = loctmp_wpts_v[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



3336    loctmp_CL_k = loctmp_wpts_h[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



3337    loctmp_CD_k = loctmp_wpts_n[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



3338    loctmp_ea = loctmp_wpts_e[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



3339  }



3340



3341  *loctmp_distance2b = (real32_T)loctmp_Cls_k;



3342  *loctmp_pic_cic_kk = loctmp_sw;



3343



3344  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3345  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3346  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3347  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3348  /* %reference point r%% */



3349  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k;



3350  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k;



3351  loctmp_mass = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea;



3352  loctmp_Cls_k = (((loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k) *



3353                   (loctmp_h_k - loctmp_CL_k) +



3354                   (loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k) *



3355                   (loctmp_n_k - loctmp_CD_k)) +



3356                  (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea) *



3357                  (loctmp_e_k - loctmp_ea)) / ((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k +



3358    loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass);



3359  loctmp_hd_k = (loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k) *



3360    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_CL_k;



3361  loctmp_nd_k = (loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k) *



3362    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_CD_k;



3363  loctmp_ed_k = (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea) *



3364    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_ea;



3365  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_hd_k;



3366  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_nd_k;



3367  loctmp_mass = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ed_k;



3368  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_b_L / sqrt((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k *



3369    loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass);



3370  *loctmp_er_k = (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ed_k) *



3371    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_ed_k;



3372  *loctmp_nr_k = (loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_nd_k) *



3373    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_nd_k;



3374  *loctmp_hr_k = (loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_hd_k) *



3375    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_hd_k;



3376



3377  /* %alpha and beta track%% */



3378  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k;



3379  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k;



3380  loctmp_mass = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea;



3381  loctmp_atrack = asin((loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k) /



3382                       sqrt((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k *



3383    loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass));



3384  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k;



3385  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea;



3386  loctmp_factor = 1;



3387  loctmp_mass = 0.0;



3388  if (!((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k > 0.0) &&



3389        (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea > 0.0))) {



3390    if ((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k > 0.0) &&



3391        (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea < 0.0)) {



3392      loctmp_mass = 3.1415926535897931;



3393      loctmp_factor = -1;



3394    } else {



3395      if ((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k < 0.0) &&



3396          (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea < 0.0)) {



3397        loctmp_mass = -3.1415926535897931;



3398        loctmp_factor = -1;



3399      }



3400    }



3401  }



3402



3403  loctmp_btrack = asin((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k) /



3404                       sqrt(loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k *



3405    loctmp_Cns_k)) * (real_T)loctmp_factor + loctmp_mass;



3406



3407  /* %edot, ndot and hdot relative to track%% */



3408  loctmp_edot_track_k = (sin(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fh_k +



3409    sin(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fn_k) + cos(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) *



3410    loctmp_fe_k;



3411  loctmp_ndot_track_k = (-sin(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fh_k



3412    + cos(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fn_k) - cos(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack)



3413    * loctmp_fe_k;



3414



3415  /* %er-e, nr-n and hr-h relative to track%% */



3416  /* %etaLon at time [k]%% */



3417  loctmp_nr_k_0[0] = *loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k;



3418  loctmp_nr_k_0[1] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;



3419  loctmp_fn_k_0[0] = loctmp_fn_k;



3420  loctmp_fn_k_0[1] = loctmp_fe_k;



3421  *loctmp_etaLon_k = rt_atan2d_snf(*loctmp_hr_k - loctmp_h_k,



3422    ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_nr_k_0)) - rt_atan2d_snf(loctmp_fh_k,



3423    ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_fn_k_0));



3424



3425  /* %etaLat at time [k]%% */



3426  loctmp_Cls_k = rt_atan2d_snf(loctmp_ndot_track_k, loctmp_edot_track_k) -



3427    rt_atan2d_snf((-sin(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_hr_k -



3428    loctmp_h_k) + (*loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k) * cos(loctmp_btrack)) - cos



3429                  (loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_er_k -



3430    loctmp_e_k), (sin(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_hr_k -



3431    loctmp_h_k) + (*loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k) * sin(loctmp_btrack)) + cos



3432                  (loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_er_k -



3433    loctmp_e_k));



3434  *loctmp_etaLat_k = loctmp_Cls_k;



3435  if (loctmp_Cls_k > 3.1415926535897931) {



3436    *loctmp_etaLat_k = loctmp_Cls_k - 6.2831853071795862;



3437  }



3438



3439  if (loctmp_Cls_k < -3.1415926535897931) {



3440    *loctmp_etaLat_k = loctmp_Cls_k + 6.2831853071795862;



3441  }



3442



3443  /* OP trajectory generation */



3444  /* reassigning Vab (based on the new d point) */



3445  if (loctmp_b_TR == 2.0) {



3446    loctmp_CL_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_n_op_k;



3447    loctmp_CD_k = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_e_op_k;



3448    loctmp_ea = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_h_op_k;



3449    loctmp_r_a = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_nd_k;



3450    loctmp_s_a = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ed_k;



3451    loctmp_t_a = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_hd_k;



3452    loctmp_mass = loctmp_nd_k - loctmp_n_op_k;



3453    loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_ed_k - loctmp_e_op_k;



3454    loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_hd_k - loctmp_h_op_k;



3455    loctmp_r_a = sqrt((loctmp_CL_k * loctmp_CL_k + loctmp_CD_k * loctmp_CD_k) +



3456                      loctmp_ea * loctmp_ea) - sqrt((loctmp_r_a * loctmp_r_a +



3457      loctmp_s_a * loctmp_s_a) + loctmp_t_a * loctmp_t_a);



3458    if (loctmp_r_a < 0.0) {



3459      loctmp_r_a = -1.0;



3460    } else if (loctmp_r_a > 0.0) {



3461      loctmp_r_a = 1.0;



3462    } else {



3463      if (loctmp_r_a == 0.0) {



3464        loctmp_r_a = 0.0;



3465      }



3466    }



3467



3468    *loctmp_Vab_k = sqrt((loctmp_vn_op_k * loctmp_vn_op_k + loctmp_ve_op_k *



3469                          loctmp_ve_op_k) + loctmp_vh_op_k * loctmp_vh_op_k) -



3470      atan(sqrt((loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass + loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k) +



3471                loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k) * loctmp_r_a / 100.0) *



3472      0.063661977236758135;



3473



3474    /* (168.78) (5) (/100) */



3475  }



3476



3477  /* %VT theta phi and beta command%% */



3478  /* %consider wind in VTcmd [0]: no [1]:yes */



3479  loctmp_mass = *loctmp_Vab_k * cos(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) + 0.0 *



3480    loctmp_sw;



3481  loctmp_Cns_k = *loctmp_Vab_k * cos(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) + 0.0 *

3486  loctmp_Cls_k = atan(*loctmp_etaLon_k * loctmp_sw);



3487  loctmp_er_k_1[0] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;

3491    loctmp_fn_k) + loctmp_fh_k * loctmp_fh_k) * 2.0 * (loctmp_Cls_k *



3492    loctmp_b_KpLon + loctmp_ro_k), ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm_h(loctmp_er_k_1));

3494  loctmp_er_k_0[1] = *loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k;



3495  *loctmp_phicmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf((loctmp_edot_track_k * loctmp_edot_track_k +



3496    loctmp_ndot_track_k * loctmp_ndot_track_k) * 2.0 * loctmp_b_KpLat *



3497    loctmp_sw * *loctmp_etaLat_k, ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_er_k_0));



3498



3499  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3500  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3501  /* %%%implementing saturation of actuators%% */



3502  /* %deflection max and min */



3503  if (loctmp_THL_k > loctmp_b_ThrottleMax) {

3535  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3536  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */

3550



3551  /* %UAV prediction%% */



3552  loctmp_Cls_k = ((loctmp_U_k * loctmp_Udot_k + loctmp_V_k * loctmp_Vdot_k) +



3553                  loctmp_W_k * loctmp_Wdot_k) / loctmp_VT_k;



3554  *loctmp_falpha_k = (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_Wdot_k - loctmp_W_k * loctmp_Udot_k) /



3555    (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_U_k + loctmp_W_k * loctmp_W_k);



3556  *loctmp_fbeta_k = (loctmp_VT_k * loctmp_Vdot_k - loctmp_V_k * loctmp_Cls_k) /



3557    (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_U_k + loctmp_W_k * loctmp_W_k) * cos(loctmp_beta_k);



3558  *loctmp_VT_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_VT_k;



3559  *loctmp_alpha_kk = loctmp_b_dt * *loctmp_falpha_k + loctmp_alpha_k;



3560  *loctmp_beta_kk = loctmp_b_dt * *loctmp_fbeta_k + loctmp_beta_k;



3561  *loctmp_phi_kk = ((loctmp_R_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) + loctmp_Q_k * sin



3562                     (loctmp_phi_k)) * tan(loctmp_theta_k) + loctmp_P_k) *



3563    loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_phi_k;



3564  *loctmp_theta_kk = (loctmp_Q_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) - loctmp_R_k * sin



3565                      (loctmp_phi_k)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_theta_k;



3566  *loctmp_psi_kk = (loctmp_R_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) + loctmp_Q_k * sin



3567                    (loctmp_phi_k)) / cos(loctmp_theta_k) * loctmp_b_dt +



3568    loctmp_psi_k;



3569  *loctmp_P_kk = ((((loctmp_b_IyyB - loctmp_b_IzzB) * loctmp_b_IzzB -



3570                    loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB) / loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_R_k



3571                   + loctmp_c2 * loctmp_P_k) * loctmp_Q_k + (loctmp_b_IzzB /



3572    loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_Cl_k + loctmp_c4 * loctmp_Cn_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



3573    loctmp_b_S * loctmp_b_b)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_P_k;



3574  *loctmp_Q_kk = (((loctmp_b_IzzB - loctmp_b_IxxB) / loctmp_b_IyyB * loctmp_P_k *



3575                   loctmp_R_k - (loctmp_P_k * loctmp_P_k - loctmp_R_k *



3576    loctmp_R_k) * (loctmp_b_IxzB / loctmp_b_IyyB)) + loctmp_Qbar_k * loctmp_b_S *



3577                  loctmp_b_Cbar * (1.0 / loctmp_b_IyyB) * loctmp_Cms_k) *



3578    loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_Q_k;



3579  *loctmp_R_kk = ((((loctmp_b_IxxB - loctmp_b_IyyB) * loctmp_b_IxxB +



3580                    loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB) / loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_P_k



3581                   - loctmp_c2 * loctmp_R_k) * loctmp_Q_k + (loctmp_b_IxxB /



3582    loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_Cn_k + loctmp_c4 * loctmp_Cl_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



3583    loctmp_b_S * loctmp_b_b)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_R_k;



3584



3585  /* %inertial frame prediction%% */



3586  *loctmp_n_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fn_k + loctmp_n_k;



3587  *loctmp_e_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fe_k + loctmp_e_k;



3588  *loctmp_h_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fh_k + loctmp_h_k;



3589



3590  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3591  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3592  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3593  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3594  /* %outputs e, y and z%% */



3595  loctmp_e_augm_k[0] = *loctmp_VTcmd_k - loctmp_VT_k;



3596  loctmp_e_augm_k[1] = *loctmp_thetacmd_k - loctmp_theta_k;



3597  loctmp_e_augm_k[2] = *loctmp_phicmd_k - loctmp_phi_k;



3598  loctmp_e_augm_k[3] = 0.0 - loctmp_beta_k;



3599



3600  /* %Robustness states at [k+1]%% */



3601  *loctmp_xw11_kk = loctmp_b_W11d.a * loctmp_xw11_k + loctmp_b_W11d.b *



3602    loctmp_e_augm_k[0];



3603



3604  /* W11 e_VT */



3605  *loctmp_xw12_kk = loctmp_b_W12d.a * loctmp_xw12_k + loctmp_b_W12d.b *



3606    loctmp_e_augm_k[1];



3607



3608  /* W12 e_theta */



3609  *loctmp_xw13_kk = loctmp_b_W13d.a * loctmp_xw13_k + loctmp_b_W13d.b *



3610    loctmp_e_augm_k[2];



3611



3612  /* W13 e_phi */



3613  *loctmp_xw14_kk = (0.0 - loctmp_beta_k) * loctmp_b_W14d.b + loctmp_b_W14d.a *



3614    loctmp_xw14_k;



3615



3616  /* W14 e_beta */



3617  *loctmp_xw21_kk = loctmp_b_W21d.a * loctmp_xw21_k + loctmp_b_W21d.b *



3618    loctmp_THLcmd_k;



3619



3620  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



3621  *loctmp_xw22_kk = loctmp_b_W22d.a * loctmp_xw22_k + loctmp_b_W22d.b *



3622    loctmp_ELcmd_k;



3623



3624  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



3625  *loctmp_xw23_kk = loctmp_b_W23d.a * loctmp_xw23_k + loctmp_b_W23d.b *



3626    loctmp_AILcmd_k;



3627



3628  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



3629  *loctmp_xw24_kk = loctmp_b_W24d.a * loctmp_xw24_k + loctmp_b_W24d.b *



3630    loctmp_RDRcmd_k;



3631



3632  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



3633  *loctmp_xw31_kk = loctmp_b_W31d.a * loctmp_xw31_k + loctmp_b_W31d.b *



3634    loctmp_VT_k;



3635



3636  /* W31 VT */



3637  *loctmp_xw32_kk = loctmp_b_W32d.a * loctmp_xw32_k + loctmp_b_W32d.b *



3638    loctmp_theta_k;



3639



3640  /* W32 theta */



3641  *loctmp_xw33_kk = loctmp_b_W33d.a * loctmp_xw33_k + loctmp_b_W33d.b *



3642    loctmp_phi_k;



3643



3644  /* W33 phi */



3645  *loctmp_xw34_kk = loctmp_b_W34d.a * loctmp_xw34_k + loctmp_b_W34d.b *



3646    loctmp_beta_k;



3647



3648  /* W34 beta */



3649  /* %Robustness output at [k] */



3650  loctmp_z_augm_k[0] = loctmp_b_W11d.c * loctmp_xw11_k + loctmp_b_W11d.d *



3651    loctmp_e_augm_k[0];



3652



3653  /* W11 e_VT */



3654  loctmp_z_augm_k[1] = loctmp_b_W12d.c * loctmp_xw12_k + loctmp_b_W12d.d *



3655    loctmp_e_augm_k[1];



3656



3657  /* W12 e_theta */



3658  loctmp_z_augm_k[2] = loctmp_b_W13d.c * loctmp_xw13_k + loctmp_b_W13d.d *



3659    loctmp_e_augm_k[2];



3660



3661  /* W13 e_phi */



3662  loctmp_z_augm_k[3] = (0.0 - loctmp_beta_k) * loctmp_b_W14d.d + loctmp_b_W14d.c



3663    * loctmp_xw14_k;



3664



3665  /* W14 e_beta */



3666  loctmp_z_augm_k[4] = loctmp_b_W21d.c * loctmp_xw21_k + loctmp_b_W21d.d *



3667    loctmp_THLcmd_k;



3668



3669  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



3670  loctmp_z_augm_k[5] = loctmp_b_W22d.c * loctmp_xw22_k + loctmp_b_W22d.d *



3671    loctmp_ELcmd_k;



3672



3673  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



3674  loctmp_z_augm_k[6] = loctmp_b_W23d.c * loctmp_xw23_k + loctmp_b_W23d.d *



3675    loctmp_AILcmd_k;



3676



3677  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



3678  loctmp_z_augm_k[7] = loctmp_b_W24d.c * loctmp_xw24_k + loctmp_b_W24d.d *



3679    loctmp_RDRcmd_k;



3680



3681  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



3682  loctmp_z_augm_k[8] = loctmp_b_W31d.c * loctmp_xw31_k + loctmp_b_W31d.d *



3683    loctmp_VT_k;



3684



3685  /* W31 VT */



3686  loctmp_z_augm_k[9] = loctmp_b_W32d.c * loctmp_xw32_k + loctmp_b_W32d.d *



3687    loctmp_theta_k;



3688



3689  /* W32 theta */



3690  loctmp_z_augm_k[10] = loctmp_b_W33d.c * loctmp_xw33_k + loctmp_b_W33d.d *



3691    loctmp_phi_k;



3692



3693  /* W33 phi */



3694  loctmp_z_augm_k[11] = loctmp_b_W34d.c * loctmp_xw34_k + loctmp_b_W34d.d *



3695    loctmp_beta_k;



3696



3697  /* W34 beta */



3698  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3699  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



3700}

4838



4839real_T rt_powd_snf(real_T loctmp_u0, real_T loctmp_u1)



4840{



4841  real_T loctmp_y;



4842  real_T loctmp_tmp;



4843  real_T loctmp_tmp_0;



4844  if (rtIsNaN(loctmp_u0) || rtIsNaN(loctmp_u1)) {



4845    loctmp_y = (rtNaN);



4846  } else {



4847    loctmp_tmp = fabs(loctmp_u0);



4848    loctmp_tmp_0 = fabs(loctmp_u1);



4849    if (rtIsInf(loctmp_u1)) {



4850      if (loctmp_tmp == 1.0) {



4851        loctmp_y = (rtNaN);



4852      } else if (loctmp_tmp > 1.0) {



4853        if (loctmp_u1 > 0.0) {



4854          loctmp_y = (rtInf);



4855        } else {



4856          loctmp_y = 0.0;



4857        }



4858      } else if (loctmp_u1 > 0.0) {



4859        loctmp_y = 0.0;



4860      } else {



4861        loctmp_y = (rtInf);



4862      }



4863    } else if (loctmp_tmp_0 == 0.0) {



4864      loctmp_y = 1.0;



4865    } else if (loctmp_tmp_0 == 1.0) {



4866      if (loctmp_u1 > 0.0) {



4867        loctmp_y = loctmp_u0;



4868      } else {



4869        loctmp_y = 1.0 / loctmp_u0;



4870      }



4871    } else if (loctmp_u1 == 2.0) {



4872      loctmp_y = loctmp_u0 * loctmp_u0;



4873    } else if ((loctmp_u1 == 0.5) && (loctmp_u0 >= 0.0)) {



4874      loctmp_y = sqrt(loctmp_u0);



4875    } else if ((loctmp_u0 < 0.0) && (loctmp_u1 > floor(loctmp_u1))) {



4876      loctmp_y = (rtNaN);



4877    } else {



4878      loctmp_y = pow(loctmp_u0, loctmp_u1);



4879    }



4880  }



4881



4882  return loctmp_y;



4883}

5209  loctmp_Vdot_k = ((loctmp_P_k * loctmp_W_k - loctmp_R_k * loctmp_U_k) +



5210                   loctmp_b_g * sin(loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_theta_k)) +



5211    loctmp_Cns_k;



5212  loctmp_Wdot_k = ((loctmp_Q_k * loctmp_U_k - loctmp_P_k * loctmp_V_k) +



5213                   loctmp_b_g * cos(loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_theta_k)) +



5214    loctmp_mass;



5215



5216  /* %inertial speed (with no wind)%% */



5217  loctmp_fn_k = ((sin(loctmp_phi_k) * sin(loctmp_theta_k) * cos(loctmp_psi_k) -



5218                  cos(loctmp_phi_k) * sin(loctmp_psi_k)) * loctmp_V_k +



5219                 loctmp_U_k * cos(loctmp_theta_k) * cos(loctmp_psi_k)) + (cos



5220    (loctmp_phi_k) * sin(loctmp_theta_k) * cos(loctmp_psi_k) + sin(loctmp_phi_k)



5221    * sin(loctmp_psi_k)) * loctmp_W_k;



5222  loctmp_fe_k = ((sin(loctmp_phi_k) * sin(loctmp_theta_k) * sin(loctmp_psi_k) +



5223                  cos(loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_psi_k)) * loctmp_V_k +



5224                 loctmp_U_k * cos(loctmp_theta_k) * sin(loctmp_psi_k)) + (cos



5225    (loctmp_phi_k) * sin(loctmp_theta_k) * sin(loctmp_psi_k) - sin(loctmp_phi_k)



5226    * cos(loctmp_psi_k)) * loctmp_W_k;



5227  loctmp_fh_k = (loctmp_U_k * sin(loctmp_theta_k) - loctmp_V_k * sin



5228                 (loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_theta_k)) - loctmp_W_k * cos



5229    (loctmp_phi_k) * cos(loctmp_theta_k);



5230



5231  /* %inertial speed%% */



5232  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5233  /* %%%uas at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5234  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5235  /* Local variable assignment */



5236  loctmp_r_a = rt_roundd_snf(loctmp_wpt_index_k);



5237  if (loctmp_r_a < 256.0) {



5238    if (loctmp_r_a >= 0.0) {



5239      *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = (uint8_T)loctmp_r_a;



5240    } else {



5241      *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 0U;



5242    }



5243  } else {



5244    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = MAX_uint8_T;



5245  }



5246



5247  loctmp_r_a = rt_roundd_snf(loctmp_home_reset_k);



5248  if (loctmp_r_a < 256.0) {



5249    if (loctmp_r_a >= 0.0) {



5250      *loctmp_home_reset_kk = (uint8_T)loctmp_r_a;



5251    } else {



5252      *loctmp_home_reset_kk = 0U;



5253    }



5254  } else {



5255    *loctmp_home_reset_kk = MAX_uint8_T;



5256  }



5257



5258  /* PIC/CIC Transition Logic: */



5259  /*  On transition to CIC or PIC, set index = 0 and current position to  */



5260  /*  current waypoint; hold current waypoint. */



5261  if ((loctmp_sw > loctmp_pic_cic_k) || (loctmp_sw == 0.0)) {



5262    loctmp_start_wpt_k[0] = loctmp_h_k;



5263    loctmp_start_wpt_k[1] = loctmp_n_k;



5264    loctmp_start_wpt_k[2] = loctmp_e_k;



5265    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 0U;



5266    *loctmp_home_reset_kk = 0U;



5267  }



5268



5269  /*  Change the waypoint index when home command */



5270  if ((loctmp_home_cmd == 1) && (loctmp_sw == 1.0) && (*loctmp_home_reset_kk ==



5271       0)) {



5272    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 23U;



5273    *loctmp_home_reset_kk = 1U;



5274  }



5275



5276  /* OP trajectory generation */



5277  /* %reassigning the a and b waypoints */



5278  if ((loctmp_b_TR == 2.0) && (*loctmp_home_reset_kk == 0)) {



5279    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = 1U;



5280    loctmp_wpts_n[(int32_T)loctmp_wpt_index_k - 1] = loctmp_n_op_k - 100.0 *



5281      loctmp_vn_op_k;



5282    loctmp_wpts_n[(int32_T)(loctmp_wpt_index_k + 1.0) - 1] = 100.0 *



5283      loctmp_vn_op_k + loctmp_n_op_k;

5285      loctmp_ve_op_k;



5286    loctmp_wpts_e[(int32_T)(loctmp_wpt_index_k + 1.0) - 1] = 100.0 *



5287      loctmp_ve_op_k + loctmp_e_op_k;



5288    loctmp_wpts_h[(int32_T)loctmp_wpt_index_k - 1] = loctmp_h_op_k - 100.0 *



5289      loctmp_vh_op_k;



5290    loctmp_wpts_h[(int32_T)(loctmp_wpt_index_k + 1.0) - 1] = 100.0 *



5291      loctmp_vh_op_k + loctmp_h_op_k;



5292  }



5293



5294  /* calculate the next waypoint index */



5295  loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(*loctmp_wpt_index_kk + 1U);



5296  if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



5297    loctmp_factor = 255;



5298  }



5299



5300  loctmp_next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)loctmp_factor;



5301



5302  /* beyond final point (fp), go to return point (rp) */



5303  if ((uint8_T)loctmp_factor > loctmp_wpts_fp) {



5304    loctmp_next_wpt_index = loctmp_wpts_rp;



5305  }



5306



5307  /* calculate distance to next waypoint */



5308  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_n_k - loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1];



5309  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_e_k - loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1];



5310  loctmp_Cls_k = sqrt(loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k);



5311



5312  /* change to next waypoint if in range */



5313  if ((loctmp_Cls_k < loctmp_b_dist2b) && (loctmp_sw == 1.0)) {



5314    /*  Do not change index if sw=0 */



5315    *loctmp_wpt_index_kk = loctmp_next_wpt_index;



5316    if (loctmp_next_wpt_index == loctmp_wpts_fp) {



5317      loctmp_next_wpt_index = loctmp_wpts_rp;



5318    } else {



5319      loctmp_factor = (int32_T)(loctmp_next_wpt_index + 1U);



5320      if ((uint32_T)loctmp_factor > 255U) {



5321        loctmp_factor = 255;



5322      }



5323



5324      loctmp_next_wpt_index = (uint8_T)loctmp_factor;



5325    }



5326  }



5327



5328  /* function outputs */



5329  if ((*loctmp_wpt_index_kk == 0) || (*loctmp_wpt_index_kk == 23)) {



5330    /*  Assign the speed of the starting segment to the speed of the first */



5331    /*  waypoint */



5332    *loctmp_Vab_k = loctmp_wpts_v[0];



5333    loctmp_CL_k = loctmp_start_wpt_k[0];



5334    loctmp_CD_k = loctmp_start_wpt_k[1];



5335    loctmp_ea = loctmp_start_wpt_k[2];



5336  } else {



5337    *loctmp_Vab_k = loctmp_wpts_v[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



5338    loctmp_CL_k = loctmp_wpts_h[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



5339    loctmp_CD_k = loctmp_wpts_n[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



5340    loctmp_ea = loctmp_wpts_e[*loctmp_wpt_index_kk - 1];



5341  }



5342



5343  *loctmp_distance2b = (real32_T)loctmp_Cls_k;



5344  *loctmp_pic_cic_kk = loctmp_sw;



5345



5346  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5347  /* %%%trajectory logic at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5348  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5349  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5350  /* %reference point r%% */



5351  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k;



5352  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k;



5353  loctmp_mass = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea;



5354  loctmp_Cls_k = (((loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k) *



5355                   (loctmp_h_k - loctmp_CL_k) +



5356                   (loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k) *



5357                   (loctmp_n_k - loctmp_CD_k)) +



5358                  (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea) *



5359                  (loctmp_e_k - loctmp_ea)) / ((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k +



5360    loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass);



5361  loctmp_hd_k = (loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k) *



5362    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_CL_k;



5363  loctmp_nd_k = (loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k) *



5364    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_CD_k;



5365  loctmp_ed_k = (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea) *



5366    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_ea;



5367  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_hd_k;



5368  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_nd_k;



5369  loctmp_mass = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ed_k;



5370  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_b_L / sqrt((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k *



5371    loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass);



5372  *loctmp_er_k = (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ed_k) *



5373    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_ed_k;



5374  *loctmp_nr_k = (loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_nd_k) *



5375    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_nd_k;



5376  *loctmp_hr_k = (loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_hd_k) *



5377    loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_hd_k;



5378



5379  /* %alpha and beta track%% */



5380  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k;



5381  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k;



5382  loctmp_mass = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea;



5383  loctmp_atrack = asin((loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CL_k) /



5384                       sqrt((loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k *



5385    loctmp_Cns_k) + loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass));



5386  loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k;



5387  loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea;



5388  loctmp_factor = 1;



5389  loctmp_mass = 0.0;



5390  if (!((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k > 0.0) &&



5391        (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea > 0.0))) {



5392    if ((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k > 0.0) &&



5393        (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea < 0.0)) {



5394      loctmp_mass = 3.1415926535897931;



5395      loctmp_factor = -1;



5396    } else {



5397      if ((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k < 0.0) &&



5398          (loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ea < 0.0)) {



5399        loctmp_mass = -3.1415926535897931;



5400        loctmp_factor = -1;



5401      }



5402    }



5403  }



5404



5405  loctmp_btrack = asin((loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_CD_k) /



5406                       sqrt(loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_Cns_k *



5407    loctmp_Cns_k)) * (real_T)loctmp_factor + loctmp_mass;



5408



5409  /* %edot, ndot and hdot relative to track%% */



5410  loctmp_edot_track_k = (sin(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fh_k +



5411    sin(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fn_k) + cos(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) *



5412    loctmp_fe_k;



5413  loctmp_ndot_track_k = (-sin(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fh_k



5414    + cos(loctmp_btrack) * loctmp_fn_k) - cos(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack)



5415    * loctmp_fe_k;



5416



5417  /* %er-e, nr-n and hr-h relative to track%% */



5418  /* %etaLon at time [k]%% */



5419  loctmp_nr_k_0[0] = *loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k;



5420  loctmp_nr_k_0[1] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;



5421  loctmp_fn_k_0[0] = loctmp_fn_k;



5422  loctmp_fn_k_0[1] = loctmp_fe_k;



5423  *loctmp_etaLon_k = rt_atan2d_snf(*loctmp_hr_k - loctmp_h_k,



5424    ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_nr_k_0)) - rt_atan2d_snf(loctmp_fh_k,



5425    ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_fn_k_0));



5426



5427  /* %etaLat at time [k]%% */



5428  loctmp_Cls_k = rt_atan2d_snf(loctmp_ndot_track_k, loctmp_edot_track_k) -



5429    rt_atan2d_snf((-sin(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_hr_k -



5430    loctmp_h_k) + (*loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k) * cos(loctmp_btrack)) - cos



5431                  (loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_er_k -



5432    loctmp_e_k), (sin(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_hr_k -



5433    loctmp_h_k) + (*loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k) * sin(loctmp_btrack)) + cos



5434                  (loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) * (*loctmp_er_k -



5435    loctmp_e_k));



5436  *loctmp_etaLat_k = loctmp_Cls_k;



5437  if (loctmp_Cls_k > 3.1415926535897931) {



5438    *loctmp_etaLat_k = loctmp_Cls_k - 6.2831853071795862;



5439  }



5440



5441  if (loctmp_Cls_k < -3.1415926535897931) {



5442    *loctmp_etaLat_k = loctmp_Cls_k + 6.2831853071795862;



5443  }



5444



5445  /* OP trajectory generation */



5446  /* reassigning Vab (based on the new d point) */



5447  if (loctmp_b_TR == 2.0) {



5448    loctmp_CL_k = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_n_op_k;



5449    loctmp_CD_k = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_e_op_k;



5450    loctmp_ea = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_h_op_k;



5451    loctmp_r_a = loctmp_wpts_n[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_nd_k;



5452    loctmp_s_a = loctmp_wpts_e[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_ed_k;



5453    loctmp_t_a = loctmp_wpts_h[loctmp_next_wpt_index - 1] - loctmp_hd_k;



5454    loctmp_mass = loctmp_nd_k - loctmp_n_op_k;



5455    loctmp_Cns_k = loctmp_ed_k - loctmp_e_op_k;



5456    loctmp_Cls_k = loctmp_hd_k - loctmp_h_op_k;



5457    loctmp_r_a = sqrt((loctmp_CL_k * loctmp_CL_k + loctmp_CD_k * loctmp_CD_k) +



5458                      loctmp_ea * loctmp_ea) - sqrt((loctmp_r_a * loctmp_r_a +



5459      loctmp_s_a * loctmp_s_a) + loctmp_t_a * loctmp_t_a);



5460    if (loctmp_r_a < 0.0) {



5461      loctmp_r_a = -1.0;



5462    } else if (loctmp_r_a > 0.0) {



5463      loctmp_r_a = 1.0;



5464    } else {

5466        loctmp_r_a = 0.0;



5467      }



5468    }



5469



5470    *loctmp_Vab_k = sqrt((loctmp_vn_op_k * loctmp_vn_op_k + loctmp_ve_op_k *



5471                          loctmp_ve_op_k) + loctmp_vh_op_k * loctmp_vh_op_k) -



5472      atan(sqrt((loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass + loctmp_Cns_k * loctmp_Cns_k) +



5473                loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_Cls_k) * loctmp_r_a / 100.0) *



5474      0.063661977236758135;



5475



5476    /* (168.78) (5) (/100) */



5477  }



5478



5479  /* %VT theta phi and beta command%% */



5480  /* %consider wind in VTcmd [0]: no [1]:yes */



5481  loctmp_mass = *loctmp_Vab_k * cos(loctmp_atrack) * sin(loctmp_btrack) + 0.0 *



5482    loctmp_sw;



5483  loctmp_Cns_k = *loctmp_Vab_k * cos(loctmp_atrack) * cos(loctmp_btrack) + 0.0 *

5486  *loctmp_VTcmd_k = sqrt((loctmp_mass * loctmp_mass + loctmp_Cns_k *

5488  loctmp_Cls_k = atan(*loctmp_etaLon_k * loctmp_sw);



5489  loctmp_er_k_1[0] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;

5491  loctmp_er_k_1[2] = *loctmp_hr_k - loctmp_h_k;



5492  *loctmp_thetacmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf(((loctmp_fe_k * loctmp_fe_k + loctmp_fn_k *



5493    loctmp_fn_k) + loctmp_fh_k * loctmp_fh_k) * 2.0 * (loctmp_Cls_k *



5494    loctmp_b_KpLon + loctmp_ro_k), ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm_h(loctmp_er_k_1));



5495  loctmp_er_k_0[0] = *loctmp_er_k - loctmp_e_k;



5496  loctmp_er_k_0[1] = *loctmp_nr_k - loctmp_n_k;



5497  *loctmp_phicmd_k = rt_atan2d_snf((loctmp_edot_track_k * loctmp_edot_track_k +

5499    loctmp_sw * *loctmp_etaLat_k, ANN_EKF_NMPC_2_norm(loctmp_er_k_0));



5500



5501  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5502  /* %%%guidance system at time [k]%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5503  /* %%%implementing saturation of actuators%% */



5504  /* %deflection max and min */



5505  if (loctmp_THL_k > loctmp_b_ThrottleMax) {

5507  } else {

5510    }



5511  }

5523  } else {

5531  } else {

5535  }



5536



5537  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5538  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5539  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5540  /* %longitudinal guidance integrator */



5541  *loctmp_ro_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_Cls_k * loctmp_b_KiLon + loctmp_ro_k;



5542



5543  /* %servos prediction%% */



5544  *loctmp_THL_kk = (loctmp_b_Athrottle * loctmp_THL_k + loctmp_b_Bthrottle *



5545                    loctmp_THLcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_THL_k;



5546  *loctmp_EL_kk = (loctmp_b_Aelevator * loctmp_EL_k + loctmp_b_Belevator *



5547                   loctmp_ELcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_EL_k;



5548  *loctmp_AIL_kk = (loctmp_b_Aaileron * loctmp_AIL_k + loctmp_b_Baileron *



5549                    loctmp_AILcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_AIL_k;



5550  *loctmp_RDR_kk = (loctmp_b_Arudder * loctmp_RDR_k + loctmp_b_Brudder *



5551                    loctmp_RDRcmd_k) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_RDR_k;



5552



5553  /* %UAV prediction%% */



5554  loctmp_Cls_k = ((loctmp_U_k * loctmp_Udot_k + loctmp_V_k * loctmp_Vdot_k) +



5555                  loctmp_W_k * loctmp_Wdot_k) / loctmp_VT_k;



5556  *loctmp_falpha_k = (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_Wdot_k - loctmp_W_k * loctmp_Udot_k) /



5557    (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_U_k + loctmp_W_k * loctmp_W_k);



5558  *loctmp_fbeta_k = (loctmp_VT_k * loctmp_Vdot_k - loctmp_V_k * loctmp_Cls_k) /



5559    (loctmp_U_k * loctmp_U_k + loctmp_W_k * loctmp_W_k) * cos(loctmp_beta_k);



5560  *loctmp_VT_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_Cls_k + loctmp_VT_k;



5561  *loctmp_alpha_kk = loctmp_b_dt * *loctmp_falpha_k + loctmp_alpha_k;



5562  *loctmp_beta_kk = loctmp_b_dt * *loctmp_fbeta_k + loctmp_beta_k;



5563  *loctmp_phi_kk = ((loctmp_R_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) + loctmp_Q_k * sin



5564                     (loctmp_phi_k)) * tan(loctmp_theta_k) + loctmp_P_k) *



5565    loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_phi_k;



5566  *loctmp_theta_kk = (loctmp_Q_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) - loctmp_R_k * sin



5567                      (loctmp_phi_k)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_theta_k;



5568  *loctmp_psi_kk = (loctmp_R_k * cos(loctmp_phi_k) + loctmp_Q_k * sin



5569                    (loctmp_phi_k)) / cos(loctmp_theta_k) * loctmp_b_dt +



5570    loctmp_psi_k;



5571  *loctmp_P_kk = ((((loctmp_b_IyyB - loctmp_b_IzzB) * loctmp_b_IzzB -



5572                    loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB) / loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_R_k



5573                   + loctmp_c2 * loctmp_P_k) * loctmp_Q_k + (loctmp_b_IzzB /



5574    loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_Cl_k + loctmp_c4 * loctmp_Cn_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



5575    loctmp_b_S * loctmp_b_b)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_P_k;



5576  *loctmp_Q_kk = (((loctmp_b_IzzB - loctmp_b_IxxB) / loctmp_b_IyyB * loctmp_P_k *



5577                   loctmp_R_k - (loctmp_P_k * loctmp_P_k - loctmp_R_k *



5578    loctmp_R_k) * (loctmp_b_IxzB / loctmp_b_IyyB)) + loctmp_Qbar_k * loctmp_b_S *



5579                  loctmp_b_Cbar * (1.0 / loctmp_b_IyyB) * loctmp_Cms_k) *



5580    loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_Q_k;



5581  *loctmp_R_kk = ((((loctmp_b_IxxB - loctmp_b_IyyB) * loctmp_b_IxxB +



5582                    loctmp_b_IxzB * loctmp_b_IxzB) / loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_P_k



5583                   - loctmp_c2 * loctmp_R_k) * loctmp_Q_k + (loctmp_b_IxxB /



5584    loctmp_delta_I * loctmp_Cn_k + loctmp_c4 * loctmp_Cl_k) * (loctmp_Qbar_k *



5585    loctmp_b_S * loctmp_b_b)) * loctmp_b_dt + loctmp_R_k;



5586



5587  /* %inertial frame prediction%% */



5588  *loctmp_n_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fn_k + loctmp_n_k;



5589  *loctmp_e_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fe_k + loctmp_e_k;



5590  *loctmp_h_kk = loctmp_b_dt * loctmp_fh_k + loctmp_h_k;



5591



5592  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5593  /* %%%prediction of kk%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5594  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5595  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5596  /* %outputs e, y and z%% */



5597  loctmp_e_augm_k[0] = *loctmp_VTcmd_k - loctmp_VT_k;



5598  loctmp_e_augm_k[1] = *loctmp_thetacmd_k - loctmp_theta_k;



5599  loctmp_e_augm_k[2] = *loctmp_phicmd_k - loctmp_phi_k;



5600  loctmp_e_augm_k[3] = 0.0 - loctmp_beta_k;



5601



5602  /* %Robustness states at [k+1]%% */



5603  *loctmp_xw11_kk = loctmp_b_W11d.a * loctmp_xw11_k + loctmp_b_W11d.b *



5604    loctmp_e_augm_k[0];



5605



5606  /* W11 e_VT */



5607  *loctmp_xw12_kk = loctmp_b_W12d.a * loctmp_xw12_k + loctmp_b_W12d.b *



5608    loctmp_e_augm_k[1];



5609



5610  /* W12 e_theta */



5611  *loctmp_xw13_kk = loctmp_b_W13d.a * loctmp_xw13_k + loctmp_b_W13d.b *



5612    loctmp_e_augm_k[2];



5613



5614  /* W13 e_phi */



5615  *loctmp_xw14_kk = (0.0 - loctmp_beta_k) * loctmp_b_W14d.b + loctmp_b_W14d.a *



5616    loctmp_xw14_k;



5617



5618  /* W14 e_beta */



5619  *loctmp_xw21_kk = loctmp_b_W21d.a * loctmp_xw21_k + loctmp_b_W21d.b *



5620    loctmp_THLcmd_k;



5621



5622  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



5623  *loctmp_xw22_kk = loctmp_b_W22d.a * loctmp_xw22_k + loctmp_b_W22d.b *



5624    loctmp_ELcmd_k;



5625



5626  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



5627  *loctmp_xw23_kk = loctmp_b_W23d.a * loctmp_xw23_k + loctmp_b_W23d.b *



5628    loctmp_AILcmd_k;



5629



5630  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



5631  *loctmp_xw24_kk = loctmp_b_W24d.a * loctmp_xw24_k + loctmp_b_W24d.b *



5632    loctmp_RDRcmd_k;



5633



5634  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



5635  *loctmp_xw31_kk = loctmp_b_W31d.a * loctmp_xw31_k + loctmp_b_W31d.b *



5636    loctmp_VT_k;



5637



5638  /* W31 VT */



5639  *loctmp_xw32_kk = loctmp_b_W32d.a * loctmp_xw32_k + loctmp_b_W32d.b *



5640    loctmp_theta_k;



5641



5642  /* W32 theta */



5643  *loctmp_xw33_kk = loctmp_b_W33d.a * loctmp_xw33_k + loctmp_b_W33d.b *



5644    loctmp_phi_k;



5645



5646  /* W33 phi */



5647  *loctmp_xw34_kk = loctmp_b_W34d.a * loctmp_xw34_k + loctmp_b_W34d.b *



5648    loctmp_beta_k;



5649



5650  /* W34 beta */



5651  /* %Robustness output at [k] */



5652  loctmp_z_augm_k[0] = loctmp_b_W11d.c * loctmp_xw11_k + loctmp_b_W11d.d *



5653    loctmp_e_augm_k[0];



5654



5655  /* W11 e_VT */



5656  loctmp_z_augm_k[1] = loctmp_b_W12d.c * loctmp_xw12_k + loctmp_b_W12d.d *



5657    loctmp_e_augm_k[1];



5658



5659  /* W12 e_theta */



5660  loctmp_z_augm_k[2] = loctmp_b_W13d.c * loctmp_xw13_k + loctmp_b_W13d.d *



5661    loctmp_e_augm_k[2];



5662



5663  /* W13 e_phi */



5664  loctmp_z_augm_k[3] = (0.0 - loctmp_beta_k) * loctmp_b_W14d.d + loctmp_b_W14d.c



5665    * loctmp_xw14_k;



5666



5667  /* W14 e_beta */



5668  loctmp_z_augm_k[4] = loctmp_b_W21d.c * loctmp_xw21_k + loctmp_b_W21d.d *



5669    loctmp_THLcmd_k;



5670



5671  /* W21 Throttle cmd */



5672  loctmp_z_augm_k[5] = loctmp_b_W22d.c * loctmp_xw22_k + loctmp_b_W22d.d *



5673    loctmp_ELcmd_k;



5674



5675  /* W22 Elevator cmd */



5676  loctmp_z_augm_k[6] = loctmp_b_W23d.c * loctmp_xw23_k + loctmp_b_W23d.d *



5677    loctmp_AILcmd_k;



5678



5679  /* W23 Aileron cmd */



5680  loctmp_z_augm_k[7] = loctmp_b_W24d.c * loctmp_xw24_k + loctmp_b_W24d.d *



5681    loctmp_RDRcmd_k;



5682



5683  /* W24 Rudder cmd */



5684  loctmp_z_augm_k[8] = loctmp_b_W31d.c * loctmp_xw31_k + loctmp_b_W31d.d *



5685    loctmp_VT_k;



5686



5687  /* W31 VT */



5688  loctmp_z_augm_k[9] = loctmp_b_W32d.c * loctmp_xw32_k + loctmp_b_W32d.d *



5689    loctmp_theta_k;



5690



5691  /* W32 theta */



5692  loctmp_z_augm_k[10] = loctmp_b_W33d.c * loctmp_xw33_k + loctmp_b_W33d.d *



5693    loctmp_phi_k;



5694



5695  /* W33 phi */



5696  loctmp_z_augm_k[11] = loctmp_b_W34d.c * loctmp_xw34_k + loctmp_b_W34d.d *



5697    loctmp_beta_k;



5698



5699  /* W34 beta */



5700  /* %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5701  /* %%%Robustness nmpc calculations%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% */



5702}
